    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Here's your chance to snag a budget-friendly project car or a parts vehicle at an unbeatable price! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant wear and mechanical issues that will require attention before it's road-ready. The exterior shows heavy wear, and the interior reflects its age and use. That said, it's a great opportunity for a handy DIYer, a mechanic looking for a project, or someone in need of parts. Priced to move \u2014 come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
